                  <summary>1 copy of Niṣāb al-ṣibyān by Muḥammad Saʿd</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2010105554 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008109073 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh88003374" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1571x-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian, Arabic</textLang>
                     <title key="work_22169">commentary on the Niṣāb al-ṣibyān of Abū Naṣr Muḥammad Badr al-Dīn Farāhī</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Untitled extensive commentary by a certain <persName key="person_f8057" role="aut">Mawlavī Muḥammad Saʿd</persName> on the famous Persian mas̲navī on Arabic vocabulary, the <title key="work_22169">Niṣāb al-ṣibyān</title> of <persName key="viaf_13150645168410622328" role="ant">Abū Naṣr Muḥammad Badr al-Dīn Farāhī</persName> (flourishing circa 617/1220). 
                        </p>
                        <p>Dated colophon: completed 12 Rabīʿ al-S̲ānī RY 19 of Emperor Muḥammad Shāh, 1149/20 August 1736. 
</p>
                        <p>Scribal nastaʿlīq. 
</p>
                        <p>Not foliated; approximately 100 folios. 
</p>
                        <p>Paper wrapper. 
</p>
                        <p>Folios partially bound; cropped, stains, wormholes, later repairs. 
</p>
                        <p>Condition fragile. 
</p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f8057">Muḥammad Saʿd</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="person_f8057">محمد سعد</persName>
